<!-- ‚ïê‚ïê OVERVIEW ‚ïê‚ïê -->
<div class="page active" id="overview">
<div class="container">
  <h2 class="page-title">Three Frameworks. One Curriculum.</h2>
  <p class="page-sub">v3 integrates three evidence-based frameworks that were previously separate. Understanding how they fit together is the key to using this curriculum effectively.</p>

  <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(auto-fit,minmax(240px,1fr));gap:1px;background:var(--sand);border-radius:12px;overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:2rem;">
    <div style="background:white;padding:1.6rem;">
      <div style="font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:0.62rem;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--sage);margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Foundation ¬∑ Weeks 1‚Äì6</div>
      <h3 style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">PERMA as the Daily Spine</h3>
      <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#555;">Seligman's five well-being pillars (Positive Emotion, Engagement, Relationships, Meaning, Accomplishment) run as <em>daily micro-exercises</em> throughout every module. PERMA-Profiler scores are taken at Week 1 and Week 12 as primary outcome measures.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background:white;padding:1.6rem;">
      <div style="font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:0.62rem;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#92400e;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Action Arc ¬∑ Weeks 7‚Äì9</div>
      <h3 style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">CAN as the 3-Week Spine</h3>
      <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#555;">Stanford's Connect ‚Üí Adapt ‚Üí Innovate framework becomes a dedicated 3-week immersive arc ‚Äî the pivot point between inner work and outer leadership. Each week is its own full module with daily practices and a major weekly challenge.</p>
    </div>
    <div style="background:white;padding:1.6rem;">
      <div style="font-family:'DM Mono',monospace;font-size:0.62rem;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:#6a8fa8;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Clinical Scaffold ¬∑ All Weeks</div>
      <h3 style="font-family:'Playfair Display',serif;font-size:1.05rem;font-weight:700;margin-bottom:0.5rem;">Cambridge as the Clinical Backbone</h3>
      <p style="font-size:0.82rem;color:#555;">The Cambridge Youth Climate Mental Health framework provides the therapeutic scaffolding ‚Äî ensuring every activity is clinically appropriate for distressed youth. Sunnie is trained to detect clinical signals and adjust accordingly.</p>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Curriculum Map -->
  <h2 class="page-title">12-Week Curriculum Map</h2>
  <p class="page-sub">The curriculum moves in three arcs: <strong>Healing</strong> (Weeks 1‚Äì4), <strong>Rooting</strong> (Weeks 5‚Äì6), and <strong>Leading</strong> (Weeks 7‚Äì12).</p>

  <div style="background:white;border-radius:12px;border:1px solid var(--sand);overflow:hidden;margin-bottom:2rem;">
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(12,1fr);height:8px;">
